{
  "title": "Fracking 1",
  "publicationStatus": "public",
  "subtitle": "Drilling for Natural Gas",
  "helpOnLoad": false,
  "aboutOnLoad": true,
  "about": [
    "Explore the process of horizontal drilling and hydraulic fracturing to release",
    "natural gas from shale layers.",
    "",
    "Press the **down** drilling button. Place your cursor at the land surface in the model, and click to start drilling.",
    "The model will scroll to show deeper layers. When you reach the shale layer containing natural gas (indicated with ",
    "moving red dots)",
    "press the **left** or **right** drilling button to drill horizontally.",
    "",
    "When you are done drilling:",
    "",
    "1. Set off explosions to fracture the shale layer.",
    "",
    "2. Fill the pipe with water or propane to hydraulically fracture the shale further.",
    "",
    "3. Pump out the fracking fluid.",
    "",
    "The graph shows methane production for each well you drill. You can drill up to three wells."
    ],
    "credits": ["This [High-Adventure Science](http://has.concord.org \"High-Adventure Science\") interactive ",
              "was developed under a series of grants from the [National Science Foundation](http://nsf.gov \"National Science Foundation\") ",
              "(DRL-0929774, DRL-1220756 ) in partnership with the ",
              "[National Geographic Society](http://nationalgeographic.org/education/ \"National Geographic Society\")."],
  "theme": ["has", "standalone-playback","graph-title-bg"],
  "aspectRatio": 1.2,
  "fontScale": 0.8,
  "models": [
    {
      "type": "iframe-model",
      "id": "iframe-model",
      "url": "models/lab-version/1/iframe-model/iframe-model.json",
      "modelOptions":{
        "url": "//models-resources.concord.org/agentscript/fracking/lab-embeddable.html#showEarthPatches",
        "drillDirection": null
      },
      "viewOptions": {
        "aspectRatio": 1.55,
        "controlButtons": "play_reset"
      },
      "onLoad": [
        "onPropertyChange('explosionPossible', function() {",
        "  setComponentDisabled('explode-btn', !get('explosionPossible'));",
        "});",
        "onPropertyChange('fillPossible', function() {",
        "  setComponentDisabled('fill-water-btn', !get('fillPossible'));",
        "  setComponentDisabled('fill-propane-btn', !get('fillPossible'));",
        "});",
        "onPropertyChange('removeFluidPossible', function() {",
        "  setComponentDisabled('pump-out-btn', !get('removeFluidPossible'));",
        "});"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "initialYear",
      "initialValue": null
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [
    {
      "name": "explosionPossible",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('explosionPossible') || false;"
    },
    {
      "name": "fillPossible",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('fillPossible') || false;"
    },
    {
      "name": "removeFluidPossible",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('removeFluidPossible') || false;"
    },
    {
      "name": "year",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('year');"
    },
    {
      "name": "graphYear",
      "value": "return get('initialYear') ? get('year') - get('initialYear') : null;"
    },
    {
      "name": "well0",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well0') || 0;"
    },
    {
      "name": "well1",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well1') || 0;"
    },
    {
      "name": "well2",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('well2') || 0;"
    },
    {
      "name": "wellsCombined",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('wellsCombined') || 0;"
    }
  ],
  "helpTips": [
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "type": "radio",
      "id": "drill",
      "orientation": "horizontal",
      "label": "Drill",
      "labelOn": "top",
      "style": "toggle",
      "property": "drillDirection",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "<i class='fa fa-long-arrow-left'></i>",
          "value": "left"
        },
        {
          "text": "<i class='fa fa-long-arrow-down'></i>",
          "value": "down"
        },
        {
          "text": "<i class='fa fa-long-arrow-right'></i>",
          "value": "right"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "explode-btn",
      "text": "Set off explosions",
      "width": "20em",
      "disabled": true,
      "action": "explode()"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "fill-water-btn",
      "text": "Fill with water",
      "width": "9em",
      "disabled": true,
      "action": "floodWater()"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "fill-propane-btn",
      "text": "Fill with propane",
      "width": "9em",
      "disabled": true,
      "action": "floodPropane()"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "id": "pump-out-btn",
      "text": "Pump out fracking fluid",
      "width": "20em",
      "disabled": true,
      "action": "pumpOut(); if (!get('initialYear')) { set('initialYear', get('year')); }"
    },
    {
      "id": "methane-graph",
      "type": "graph",
      "properties": [
        "well0",
        "well1",
        "well2",
        "wellsCombined"
      ],
      "xProperty": "graphYear",
      "title": "Methane Production",
      "titlePosition": "left",
      "buttonsLayout": "horizontal",
      "buttonsStyle": "text",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "100%",
      "enableAxisScaling": false,
      "enableZooming": false,
      "xlabel": "Time (years)",
      "xmin": 0,
      "xmax": 40,
      "ylabel": "Methane",
      "ymin": 0,
      "ymax": 600,
      "xTickCount": 6,
      "yTickCount": 6,
      "xFormatter": "d",
      "yFormatter": ".2r",
      "dataColors": [
        "#d95f02",
        "#1b9e77",
        "#7570B3",
        "#000000"
      ],
      "legendLabels": [
        "Well 1",
        "Well 2",
        "Well 3",
        "Combined"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "playback",
      "type": "playback",
      "stepping": true
    }
  ],
   "layout": {
     "playback-container": [
      "playback"
    ],
    
    "bottom-1": [
      "drill"
    ],
    "bottom-2": [
      "explode-btn"
    ],
    "bottom-3": [
      
        "fill-water-btn"
      ,
      
        "fill-propane-btn"
      
    ],
    "bottom-4": [
      "pump-out-btn"
    ],
    "right": [
      "methane-graph"
    ]
  },
  "template": [
     {
      "id": "playback-container",
      "top": "model.bottom",
      "left": "model.left"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottom-1",
      "left": "model.left",
      "top": "playback-container.bottom",
      "padding-top": "0.8em"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottom-2",
      "left": "model.left",
      "top": "bottom-1.bottom",
      "padding-top": "1.5em"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottom-3",
      "left": "model.left",
      "top": "bottom-2.bottom",
      "padding-top": "0.5em"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottom-4",
      "left": "model.left",
      "top": "bottom-3.bottom",
      "padding-top": "0.5em"
    },
    {
      "id": "right",
      "width": "model.width * 0.55",
      "height": "model.height",
      "left": "model.right",
      "top": "model.top",
      "padding-left": "0.3em"
    }
  ]
}
